    "description": "<strong>Once upon a time... ...STONE.</strong><br><br><strong>A STONE</strong> cannot move by itself.<br><br>In fact, we cannot tell whether the <strong>STONE</strong> has the will to go up or not.<br>But we raise the <strong>STONE</strong> to the sky. That's because it's a <strong>game</strong>.<br><br><strong>Impossible Stone Game</strong> presents a new type of platform game.<br>You move the stone by applying shock waves with bombs to the stone that cannot move.<br><br>There are various obstacles on the rainbow-colored journey of the stone to the sky.<br>Beautiful but annoying obstacles that appear according to each theme will try to block the journey.<br>What kind of reward will the stone receive when it overcomes adversity through numerous falls?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A 2D platform game with a completely new control method.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simple and easy to understand, but challenging and difficult gameplay.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Minimal level design with various themes that are tightly woven.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>8-bit retro graphic design and fun chiptune music that matches the design.</li></ul>",
